settings.name: Loader
settings.description:
Change which algorithm loads specific parts of the app. Faster algorithm may not have as much information (e.g. author name may be missing).
The `Everything` option loads everything, which is very slow.
The Most things loads at a medium speed and loads everything but the thumbnails on the authours, which is why it is recommended
And Just the necesities loads really fast (~1 sec) but only loads the picture, the title of the song and half the time the author name. Other things will be missing
